{"tid":2478234,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人長假後，又成功破壞大自然","createTime":"2021-04-07T01:50:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T02:29:02.000Z","uid":5843,"like":42,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"e729cc337aab676d3f97ab2ada0c461b944bfb50","tid":2478234,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T01:50:33.000Z","msg":"呢度只係冰山一角，聽講西貢都好撚癲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcMvMr8bkfwvM7zwRKSEPJVsEYZhrnA88H2f9PgXHQ5wW?filename=UyJBccR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUyJBccR.png&h=aaa7664c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWE8NwzKz1YBpWsANmbUjVBUbMEtNv2v763QyJhuzycVs?filename=PLED9Zx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPLED9Zx.png&h=ea611db9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZWt21PsfbekEqKjcqJhAKthpKjkqtSMecPq2rJePLiEy?filename=8ZkjUrd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8ZkjUrd.jpg&h=c096b1a9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPMSSDxtRipfwGb7vEjo7CFNRPsdgJumkLqnatiWV5ohS?filename=RfhKk6e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRfhKk6e.jpg&h=0addd236&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2a70ffe4408918779b802262c53f13c386ba4d65","tid":2478234,"uid":5843,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T01:52:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.vairhk.com/articles/leave-no-trace\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vairhk.com%2Farticles%2Fleave-no-trace&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtC%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=3e874583\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.vairhk.com/articles/leave-no-trace</a><br />\n<br />\n三：妥善棄置廢物 (Dispose of Waste Properly)<br />\n<br />\n相信大家對「自己垃圾，自己帶走」都唔會陌生。香港大部分郊野公園內嘅垃圾桶都已經被移除，但即使郊外有垃圾桶，其實都係隔一段時間先會有工人或義工清理，逐袋垃圾沿山徑搬落山；將垃圾帶翻市區先棄置唔單止減低對環境嘅污染，同時可以減輕清潔工人嘅負擔。<br />\n<br />\n好多人以為蕉皮同蘋果芯等廚餘可以自然分解，就隨手丢棄係野外；但其實一塊蕉皮要幾個月嘅時間先會分解，過程中有可能引嚟野生動物嚟覓食，所以都係唔好隨地扔，袋住佢拎翻市區垃圾桶先棄置。<br />\n<br />\n小編建議大家帶一個垃圾袋，將廢物裝好再帶翻市區先回收或棄置。當然啦，最好嘅方法都係減少製造垃圾，例如自己帶備水樽善用加水站，已經可以慳翻幾個膠樽。千其千其唔好亂拋垃圾，尤其係口罩！"},{"pid":"955eeb63e3f1a0054d5753e0a497103d57409665","tid":2478234,"uid":8014,"like":5,"dislike":11,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T01:52:27.000Z","msg":"一定係新香港人做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1c93a0fcbf9629702f9c1d9b115b687dbf3e6fb","tid":2478234,"uid":231480,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T01:53:53.000Z","msg":"啲人所謂親親大自然，做咩山系女孩懶係嘢咁<br />\n計我話要保護大自然，就咩郊野公園都唔好去"},{"pid":"fd1013472563bc7ea9aeba1517de13ddbe68593a","tid":2478234,"uid":5159,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T01:55:01.000Z","msg":"連登仔: 所有露營撚都係藍絲 通通割席 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1a596f29dfbde4928a440feba6598824caa156e","tid":2478234,"uid":88166,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T01:56:13.000Z","msg":"Leave no trace真係咁難？"},{"pid":"540d937f246342a48808cfdab09158760ec0d504","tid":2478234,"uid":5843,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T01:57:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNoDKNBNsqLosJy5YYTsqFfvfpuqagbMd1bxKAn6CCfXb?filename=8DvjUtU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8DvjUtU.png&h=5b20d5a6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZXpwXb7QP8XFXtRHvvUu1MWWHxe3BMTog2kuTzcyM4UT?filename=ffzpk8V.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fffzpk8V.png&h=edd221b0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qme77GF8DMk4k2bdMWZafFBo4pqikZJXRP36rmkPdepvem?filename=3WdBcfA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3WdBcfA.png&h=de839ef7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"93b